’Ů@ec7ca19a1b2a49069b47c2346ea0aee93477a9fd37e4988713a6090101151074ŮĂTitle: title: is-terminal
Path: Flags
Content:
``--stdin, -i``
: Check if stdin is a terminal.
``--stdout, -o``
: Check if stdout is a terminal.
``--stderr, -e``
: Check if stderr is a terminal.
